  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [Infra_LoadBalancer] --> Login: User Credentials\n    Login --> TokensGenerated: Success\n    \n    state TokensGenerated {Infra_RedisCache] --> AccessToken_Stateless\n        [Infra_EtcdCluster] --> RefreshToken_Stateful\n    }\n    \n    AccessToken_Stateless --> Active: valid for 15m\n    Active --> Expired: after 15m\n    Expired --> Refresh: use RefreshToken\n    \n    RefreshToken_Stateful --> StoredInDB: Active for 7d\n    StoredInDB --> Rotated: Refresh RPC called\n    Rotated --> DeletedFromDB: Old Token\n    Rotated --> StoredInDB: New Token Pair Issued\n    \n    StoredInDB --> Revoked: DeleteUser called\n    Revoked --> [Infra_EtcdCluster]\n    \n    Expired --> [Infra_RedisCache]\n",
