  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的认证令牌生命周期图。用户从负载均衡器进来，用凭证登录成功后生成一对Token——无状态的AccessToken放在Redis里，有状态的RefreshToken存在Etcd集群。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Login",
        "TokensGenerated",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，TokensGenerated是一个复合状态，里面同时包含AccessToken和RefreshToken的存储位置。那AccessToken的有效期怎么体现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TokensGenerated",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "AccessToken只有15分钟有效期，从Active到Expired。Expired之后不能直接用，必须走Refresh流程，用RefreshToken去换新的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "Active",
        "Expired",
        "Refresh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把AccessToken的状态流转画好了：Stateless的Token进入Active状态，15分钟后变Expired，然后指向Refresh动作。现在处理RefreshToken那边？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "Active",
        "Expired",
        "Refresh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RefreshToken是Stateful的，存在数据库里，默认7天有效。但有个关键机制：每次调用Refresh RPC，旧Token会被标记为Rotated，然后从数据库删除；同时签发新的Token Pair，新RefreshToken重新进入StoredInDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RefreshToken_Stateful",
        "StoredInDB",
        "Rotated",
        "DeletedFromDB",
        "TokensGenerated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以Rotated之后分两条线：一条到DeletedFromDB表示旧Token清理，另一条回到StoredInDB表示新Token入库。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rotated",
        "DeletedFromDB",
        "StoredInDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。另外还要考虑撤销场景：如果用户主动注销或者管理员删除用户，StoredInDB的Token直接变Revoked，然后清理Etcd里的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StoredInDB",
        "Revoked",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画完了。最后Expired的AccessToken也需要回收到Redis吧？我加了一条从Expired指向Infra_RedisCache的线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Expired",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，Rotated到StoredInDB的标注要改一下，应该是\"New Token Pair Issued\"而不是简单的\"New Token\"，因为AccessToken也会一起刷新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rotated",
        "StoredInDB",
        "TokensGenerated"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正标注。现在整个状态图完整了：从负载均衡器登录，双Token生成，AccessToken短周期失效后刷新，RefreshToken长周期轮换，支持主动撤销。",
      "elements_involved": [
